snippet.title: Sonic Frontiers: Sonic's Birthday Bash Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Celebrate Sonic’s birthday on the festively decorated Starfall Islands! Spin dash your way to the party with new challenges, moves, collectible Koco, and New Game +! Sonic’s Birthday Bash Update for Sonic Frontiers is available later today for free!

Follow our social channels to stay up-to-date on the latest Sonic happenings:

https://twitter.com/sonic_hedgehog
https://facebook.com/sonic
https://instagram.com/sonicthehedgehog
